1
00:00:02,300 --> 00:00:03,630
Come on,Joey!
乔伊，快说啦

2
00:00:03,870 --> 00:00:06,270
I told you everything I knew last night.
我知道的部分昨晚都告诉你了

3
00:00:06,500 --> 00:00:09,200
It's not that big a deal. So they're doing it.
摩妮卡和钱德搞在一起又怎样

4
00:00:10,340 --> 00:00:13,000
I cannot believe you would say that!
你居然这么说

5
00:00:13,210 --> 00:00:16,940
Sorry. Monica and Chandler are "making love."
抱歉 摩妮卡和钱德在“做爱”

6
00:00:18,050 --> 00:00:21,710
No,I mean,come on. This is a huge deal!
不是啦，我是说这是大事耶

7
00:00:21,980 --> 00:00:24,880
I need more details. Who initiated the first kiss?
我想知道细节 是谁先吻谁的？

8
00:00:25,390 --> 00:00:26,380
I don't know.
不知

9
00:00:27,590 --> 00:00:30,390
God,I just can't imagine Chandler being romantic.
我无法想像钱德浪漫的样子

10
00:00:32,660 --> 00:00:34,720
Is he romantic with her?
他跟她在一起时浪漫吗？

11
00:00:35,060 --> 00:00:36,050
I don't know.
不知

12
00:00:38,230 --> 00:00:39,500
Are they in love?
他们相爱吗？

13
00:00:40,340 --> 00:00:41,320
I don't know.
不知

14
00:00:43,170 --> 00:00:44,600
You don't know anything.
你什么都不知道

15
00:00:44,840 --> 00:00:45,900
I know one thing. What？
我知道一件事 什么事？

16
00:00:46,740 --> 00:00:47,970
They did it right there.
他们在这张沙发上做过

17
00:00:50,410 --> 00:00:52,180
